  %% Diagram 67A: Social Commerce Business-Friendly Attribution Map

  Connect[Vendor connects Facebook, TikTok, and YouTube channels]
  Sync[Catalog sync keeps social listings up to date]
  Engage[Shoppers interact through videos, lives, and affiliate links]
  Order[Valid interactions become attributed orders]
  Payout[Attribution and commission payout signals are recorded]

  Retry[Failed sync items are retried automatically]
  Review[Invalid codes or fraud-like activity go to review]

  Connect --> Sync --> Engage --> Order --> Payout
  Sync --> Retry --> Sync
  Engage --> Review --> Payout
